Code respository for the Head Replacement / Virtual Surgeon / Identity Transfer project

Building
--------
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=. ..

(should build on Win32, MacOS X, and linux)

Prerequisites
-------------
OpenCV 2.3.x+
GMM
GraphCut Optimization (libGCO) 2.x+
tclap 1.2.x+
libcurl
libfltk 3.x+
OpenGL [Optional: GLSL shaders support]

Running
-------
./{Build_DIR}/HeadReplacement


